<!-- ══════ INTRO ══════ -->
<section id="intro">
  <div class="intro-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Repairs & Renovations</span></div>
      <h2 class="section-title">FIX IT.<br>FINISH IT.<br>MAKE IT RIGHT.</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule"></div>
      <p class="intro-quote">"Some things just need to get done. We're the team that <em>actually shows up</em>."</p>
      <p class="intro-body">Whether it's a leaky patch of drywall, a bathroom that hasn't been touched since the '90s, or a growing punch list that keeps getting longer, ETRA Pro Services handles the repairs and renovations that keep your Halifax home running and looking its best.</p>
      <p class="intro-body">We work across the full spectrum of residential repairs and remodels. From quick handyman fixes in Dartmouth to full single-room renovations in Bedford, our approach is the same: show up on time, do quality work, and leave the space better than we found it. Homeowners across HRM trust us because we treat every project with the same level of care, whether it takes two hours or two weeks.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="intro-body">Every home needs attention over time. Trim that's been dinged up, a kitchen backsplash that's seen better days, water damage that keeps getting put off. We understand that most people don't call a contractor for the small stuff because they're worried it's not worth anyone's time. That's where we're different.</p>
      <p class="intro-body" style="color:var(--mist);font-weight:400;">No job is too small for ETRA. We genuinely mean that. A single shelf install, a door replacement, a patch and paint in the hallway. If it needs doing, we'll do it right.</p>
      <p class="intro-body">We serve Halifax, Dartmouth, Bedford, Sackville, Fall River, Cole Harbour, and all communities throughout the Halifax Regional Municipality. Free quotes, honest pricing, and a team that respects your space.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:28px;">
        <a href="#quote-form" class="btn-gold">Request Your Free Quote &nbsp;&rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════ SERVICE DETAILS ══════ -->
<section id="details">
  <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">What We Repair & Renovate</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-title">OUR REPAIR &<br>RENOVATION SERVICES</h2>
  <div class="gold-rule"></div>
  <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--ash);max-width:580px;line-height:1.9;">From a single fix to a complete room transformation, here's what we handle for homeowners across Halifax and HRM.</p>

  <div class="details-grid">
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9745;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Punch-List Repairs</div>
      <p class="detail-body">All those little things that have been piling up: squeaky doors, cracked trim, loose railings, scuffed walls, sticky drawers. We knock out your entire list efficiently so you can stop thinking about it. Popular across Halifax and Dartmouth for move-in and move-out touch-ups.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9632;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Single-Room Renovations</div>
      <p class="detail-body">Want to transform a spare bedroom, refresh a dated living room, or convert a basement space? We handle full single-room renovations from demo to finishing touches. New flooring, fresh drywall, updated trim, paint-ready walls. One room at a time, done right.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9671;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Bathroom Remodels</div>
      <p class="detail-body">From vanity swaps and tile updates to complete gut-and-rebuild bathroom renovations. We handle flooring, walls, fixtures, and finishing. Whether it's a half-bath refresh in Bedford or a full ensuite remodel in Halifax, we deliver clean, modern results.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9670;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Kitchen Updates</div>
      <p class="detail-body">Not every kitchen needs a $60K renovation. We specialize in smart, targeted kitchen updates: new backsplash, cabinet refacing, countertop replacement, updated hardware, and flooring transitions. Real improvements that change the feel of the room without blowing your budget.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9998;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">General Handyman Work</div>
      <p class="detail-body">Shelving, door installs, weatherstripping, fixture swaps, minor framing, closet organizers, and more. If you've got a project that needs a skilled set of hands, we're the call to make. Serving all of HRM with reliable, same-week scheduling whenever possible.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9679;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Water Damage Repair</div>
      <p class="detail-body">Water damage doesn't wait, and neither should your repair. We handle drywall replacement, subfloor repair, mould remediation prep, trim restoration, and moisture-damaged flooring throughout Halifax and Dartmouth. We get to the root of the issue and fix it properly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1; max-width: 100%;">
      <span class="detail-icon">&#9653;</span>
      <div class="detail-title">Trim & Finishing Work</div>
      <p class="detail-body">Baseboards, crown moulding, window casings, door trim, wainscoting, and custom millwork finishing. The trim is what makes a room look finished and professional. Whether you're completing a renovation or upgrading the details in an older Halifax home, our trim work is precise and paint-ready. We take pride in tight mitre cuts, seamless joints, and clean lines that bring a space together.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

